In a recent party congress, general secretary Alimin has handed over his post to D.N. Aidit, head of the Leninist Wing. It has become clear that the <span style="color: #c00000;">**PKI**</span> has shifted more radical.

Now with Aidit at the helm, the <span style="color: #c00000;">**PKI**</span> begins its "rejuvenation". Its labor federation, <span class="tooltip-text" title="Central All-Indonesian Worker's Organization">SOBSI</span>, saw a surge in membership and its new media organ, <span class="tooltip-text" title="People's Voice">*Soeara Rakjat*</span>, has begun mass publishing their daily newspaper. 

